{"tid":388031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捐咗 ＄１００ 去在囚抗爭者支援基金 2017-09-05","createTime":"2017-09-05T06:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T07:33:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77e88c39be071b6d92945793316738e540cf722f","tid":388031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"捐咗 ＄１００ 去在囚抗爭者支援基金 2017-09-05<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7xys3agf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7xys3agf&h=018a1a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57167297&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57167297%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7dc5257e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57167297%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&h=dfe35d6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57167297&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904</a><br />\n<br />\n【聲援良心犯】在囚抗爭者支援基金成立 吳靄儀任信託人之一<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-09-04 13:50:20 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n數以萬計港人上月20日逼爆灣仔，聲援重奪公民廣場案、反東北案等被政府窮追猛打下淪為階下囚的16名人士，用行動告訴「政府良心犯」，他們從不孤單。主辦單位當日指參與遊行人數遠超預期，是自傘運後最多港人出席的遊行集會。社民連、香港眾志、大專政關、東北支援組當日收到市民約253萬元捐款，為妥善安排運用捐款，決成立「在囚抗爭者支援基金」，4個團體同意上述遊行所籌得之款項全數撥捐本基金，作為首筆捐款。<br />\n<br />\n3名基金信託人為前立法會議員吳靄儀、嶺南大學文化研究系副教授許寶強、杜耀明。基金會用於在囚者日用品物資、法律費用、親友探監交通費及定額支援金等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://holland.pk/3qlt4g1p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3qlt4g1p&h=8b57cd84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捐款戶口(香港職工會聯盟戶口)︰恆生銀行︰295-164578-009<br />\n<br />\n戶口英文名：Hong Kong Confederation of Trade Unions"},{"pid":"2417416352b42bf2ceb442a3c3abd19900d225b1","tid":388031,"uid":60404,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:53:53.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"916ed945545ca98420896180a9635a60d895d725","tid":388031,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"旺角義士比呢16人更需要錢"},{"pid":"56725017d0593bb793a4595c9b2391880b0ee511","tid":388031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"在囚抗爭者支援基金  facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/iasfhk/?hc_ref=ARRZTWbDIO3b83c_7IwfwkfuKtznU_osMuesamfvBwm4Bo3_w86YNBflIFuPGXd8KCo&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fiasfhk%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DARRZTWbDIO3b83c_7IwfwkfuKtznU_osMuesamfvBwm4Bo3_w86YNBflIFuPGXd8KCo%26fref%3Dnf&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=768c556e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/iasfhk/?hc_ref=ARRZTWbDIO3b83c_7IwfwkfuKtznU_osMuesamfvBwm4Bo3_w86YNBflIFuPGXd8KCo&amp;fref=nf</a>"},{"pid":"6f1a284a9dbea739be65e31623bd5c9fa7ca7f7b","tid":388031,"uid":60281,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旺角義士比呢16人更需要錢</blockquote><br />\n遊行個日又叫人不分派系<br />\n到捐錢就分得清清楚楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1429724629335ec72f92fba19b85b4a13cf6038","tid":388031,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>旺角義士比呢16人更需要錢</blockquote><br />\n遊行個日又叫人不分派系<br />\n到捐錢就分得清清楚楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泛民大台：你係民，我係主，我可以割席，但你一定要撐我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n和解？無誠意和條撚咩？"}]}